    <reference type="string">&lt;p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"&gt;This service offering is a limited release to the HP IT organization. Additional communications will be distributed in Q3 &amp;nbsp;highlighting the company-wide release.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"&gt;&lt;b style="box-sizing: border-box;"&gt;To install Lync Mobile 2013 on your Windows phone:&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ol style="box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px;"&gt;
	&lt;li style="box-sizing: border-box;"&gt;
		&lt;p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;You must have&amp;nbsp;&lt;font color="#007dba"&gt;&lt;span style="box-sizing: border-box; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;"&gt;HP Mobile Access&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&amp;nbsp;to use Lync 2013 Mobile.&lt;/p&gt;
	&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li style="box-sizing: border-box;"&gt;
		&lt;p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;Open the&amp;nbsp;&lt;b style="box-sizing: border-box;"&gt;App Store&lt;/b&gt;&amp;nbsp;in your Windows Phone device.&lt;/p&gt;
	&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li style="box-sizing: border-box;"&gt;
		&lt;p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"&gt;â€‹ &amp;nbsp; In the Search tab, type&amp;nbsp;&lt;b style="box-sizing: border-box;"&gt;Lync 2013&lt;/b&gt;&amp;nbsp;and click to search&lt;b style="box-sizing: border-box;"&gt;.&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
	&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li style="box-sizing: border-box;"&gt;
		&lt;p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;Tap on the&amp;nbsp;&lt;b style="box-sizing: border-box;"&gt;Lync 2013&lt;/b&gt;&amp;nbsp;search result and tap&amp;nbsp;&lt;b style="box-sizing: border-box;"&gt;Install&lt;/b&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
	&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li style="box-sizing: border-box;"&gt;
		&lt;p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;Installation will begin. Once the application installation is complete, locate the application in the Windows start menu and tap it to open.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
	&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li style="box-sizing: border-box;"&gt;
		&lt;p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;On the welcome screen, enter your&amp;nbsp;&lt;b style="box-sizing: border-box;"&gt;HP email address&amp;nbsp;&lt;/b&gt;and&lt;b style="box-sizing: border-box;"&gt;&amp;nbsp;password&lt;/b&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
	&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li style="box-sizing: border-box;"&gt;
		&lt;p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;Then click on&amp;nbsp;&lt;b style="box-sizing: border-box;"&gt;Show Advanced Options&lt;/b&gt;.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
	&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li style="box-sizing: border-box;"&gt;
		&lt;p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;Ensure that the&amp;nbsp;&lt;b style="box-sizing: border-box;"&gt;Auto-Detect Server&lt;/b&gt;&amp;nbsp;is turned&amp;nbsp;&lt;b style="box-sizing: border-box;"&gt;on&lt;/b&gt;, and tap the&amp;nbsp;&lt;b style="box-sizing: border-box;"&gt;check&lt;/b&gt;&amp;nbsp;to sign in.&lt;/p&gt;
	&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li style="box-sizing: border-box;"&gt;
		&lt;p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;Expect a&amp;nbsp;&lt;b style="box-sizing: border-box;"&gt;1-2 minute&lt;/b&gt;&amp;nbsp;log in time -&amp;nbsp;this will depend on your network strength.&amp;nbsp;&lt;b style="box-sizing: border-box;"&gt;Note&lt;/b&gt;:&amp;nbsp;You may need to tap&amp;nbsp;the screen periodically to prevent it from going to power save mode.&lt;/p&gt;
	&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li style="box-sizing: border-box;"&gt;
		&lt;p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;Enter the phone number of your mobile device and tap&amp;nbsp;&lt;b style="box-sizing: border-box;"&gt;Next&lt;/b&gt;.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
	&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li style="box-sizing: border-box;"&gt;
		&lt;p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;Setup is complete.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
	&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"&gt;All mobile devices accessing HP corporate data must meet HP Security standards, which included installing the approved Mobile Device Management.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;</reference>
